name: JungleTac ROM File
summary: A JGC file contains a ROM image of a video game for Dingoo A320, a Chinese handheld gaming console released in 2009. It contains an exact copy of a game developed by JungleTac, which is a Chinese company that creates 8-bit and 16-bit games and consoles.
